name: • Interlude "1004" •
description: Last day before moving up a level, last chance to pretend it's still time, last chance to reflect and give thanks for a year full of life.  I want to listen to "1004 km" all day long, but is it wise? or is it just the interlude of something bigger, I don't know, and for today I don't want to know.  "No será para siempre" said the lyrics while the guitars were playing, a sobbing of the soul and a caress for the ear, perfect for this day, or maybe I'm just romanticizing a date with no real relevance, I don't know, but it's never a bad time to have an interlude...
